ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
Subject2003-2004 - TRANSFER UNDISTRIBUTED BALANCES ** Barley **
PrecisOrder authorizing the CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD (a) to adjust its accounts as of December 31, 2010, by transferring the undistributed funds in the 2003-2004 pool account for Barley to a separate account; and (b) to pay to the persons who are entitled to receive payments the amount to which they are entitled out of the separate account.
